  } = props;
 
  let { avatar } = props;

  let LeftIconWrapper = leftIconOnPress || leftIconOnLongPress
    ? TouchableHighlight
    : View;
  Iif (component) {
    Component = component;
  }
  if (typeof avatar === 'string') {
    avatar = { uri: avatar };

  return (
    <Component

      {...attributes}
